text: All other social issues stem from the breakdown of the family #Opp4All
I am convinced that if we can rediscover just a small fraction of indomitable spirit, our great nation can once again sail majestically

The fertile soil is not Washington – it is rather with your families, your neighborhoods, your communities and your churches #Opp4All
Discernment, compassion, and engagement – it is about building relationships with those who don’t see the world the way that we do #Opp4All
It's important that we don't just talk at people. Rather, we should talk with people to make a difference. #Opp4All
Communicate why life matters, why educational choice matters, & why the govt is better at creating more harm than it is at providing help
NO, it's not in found in two Corinthians but rather one Corinthians, or what most of us would refer to as 1st Corinthians...
If I care for my fellow man, there’s a patience that I am willing to exhibit because I hope to share these truths #Opp4All
At the heart of discernment is compassion. #Opp4All

text: Sharing the truth in the wrong tone or context is not always the best strategy. #Opp4All
As our liberties erode, we must be prepared to get angry and hold the line. #Opp4All
we are pounding our children to view the world through the lens of the latest “acceptable” buzzwords; tolerance and political correctness.
Why shouldn’t we be angry? The majority of our classrooms have become little more than progressive think tanks promoting extreme secularism
I am convinced that there is a how, but we must use surgical-like precision to successfully weave the social values back into our society.
Are we satisfied with continuing to take our message to the same people day after day? It’s always easier to preach to the choir. #Opp4All
We have drifted away from the values that were etched into our founding documents #Opp4All
How do I know this? I’ve lived it. Cleveland, New York & Baltimore. Hope - That’s exactly why we are gathered in this room. Hope. #Opp4All
Until we refocus on these values like life, community, education, & the family, the American people will still be hungry for hope. #Opp4All

If we truly believe in such noble things like life & #Opp4All, then we must eliminate every taxpayer dollar from funding Planned Parenthood
If we will not fight for the most basic right of life, what else are we going to fight for? #Opp4All
The American Dream is social in its nature, and it begins with life #Opp4All
We cannot deny that the federal government has hijacked the American Dream and the family has been decimated #Opp4All
